Requires: ruby, rubygems, erb, sinatra, dm-core, dm-sqlite-adapter (or whatever Data Mapper adapter you might want)

To Run: ruby register.rb, or your use your favourite rack compatible server

Edit the files at /views to fit your needs, or check out register.rb for more options.